4 HR____ COMMENDING AND CONGRATULATING THE VESTAVIA HILLS HIGH
5 SCHOOL SPEECH AND DEBATE TEAM FOR WINNING ITS FIFTH
6 CONSECUTIVE STATE CHAMPIONSHIP.
7
8 WHEREAS, highest congratulations are herein proudly
9 presented to the Vestavia Hills High School Speech and
10 Debate Team, of Vestavia Hills, Alabama, for winning its
11 fifth consecutive state championship in speech and debate at
12 the 2026 Alabama State Tournament; and
13 WHEREAS, the tournament was held March 6-7, 2026, at
14 Northridge High School in Tuscaloosa, Alabama, where the
15 Vestavia Hills team once again distinguished itself through
16 superior preparation, poise, and performance; and
17 WHEREAS, students earned state titles and top
18 finishes across multiple events, including Dev Patel in
19 Congressional Debate House A; Kaylee Zhao in Congressional
20 Debate House B and Impromptu Speaking; Veronica Zhang in
21 Congressional Debate Senate and International Extemporaneous
22 Speaking; Tina Gao in United States Extemporaneous Speaking;
23 Mina Hu in Lincoln-Douglas Debate; Abigail Wang and Anthony
24 Li in JV Public Forum Debate; and Varsity Public Forum
25 Debate championships were earned by Kaylee Zhao and Astha
26 Mehta, with co-champion honors also earned by Arhaan Lalani
27 and Vivian Shi; and
28 WHEREAS, the 2026 championship follows Vestavia
Page 1

WHEREAS, the 2026 championship follows Vestavia
