29 Hills' 2025 4th consecutive state title, reflecting a
30 sustained standard of excellence and bringing honor to
31 Vestavia Hills High School, Vestavia Hills City Schools, and
32 the State of Alabama; and
33 WHEREAS, the program has been ably led by Coach Nate
34 Conoly, whose leadership has guided Vestavia Hills students
35 to continued success in one of the most demanding forms of
36 academic competition; and
37 WHEREAS, the team's present achievements continue a
38 long and proud tradition of excellence established by
39 generations of Vestavia Hills debaters and coaches, and the
40 program has earned recognition at both the state and
41 national levels for cultivating scholarship, discipline, and
42 civic-minded leadership; and
43 WHEREAS, the achievements of the Vestavia Hills High
44 School Speech and Debate Team reflect the highest ideals of
45 academic competition and serve as a tremendous source of
46 pride to the students, coaches, families, faculty, alumni,
47 and the entire Vestavia Hills community; now therefore,
48 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF
49 THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That the Vestavia Hills High
50 School Speech and Debate Team and its coaches are hereby
51 highly honored and commended for winning their fifth
52 consecutive state championship, and this resolution is
53 dedicated to them with utmost admiration, together with
54 sincere best wishes for continued success in all future
55 endeavors.
